dcterms:description: The dataset is derived from the study conducted by Andreas Scholl, Daniel Schiffner, and Natalie Kiesler, which analyzed chat protocols submitted by 213 students who interacted with ChatGPT-3.5 during their programming exercises.
dcterms:title: Chat Protocols of Novice Programmers

dcterms:description: The dataset consists of 2335 prompts collected from students as they interacted with ChatGPT-3.5 while completing programming tasks in an introductory course at Goethe University during the winter term 2023/24.
dcterms:title: ChatGPT-3.5 Interaction Data
